sequenceDiagram
    participant V as Voter (Mobile)
    participant A as API Gateway
    participant VS as Vote Service
    participant D as Database

    V->>A: Submit Vote (Token, Selections)
    A->>VS: Validate Token
    VS->>D: Check Ballot Status
    D-->>VS: Active
    VS->>D: Record Votes (Transaction)
    VS->>D: Mark Ballot Consumed
    VS-->>V: Vote Success Confirmation
